---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="企業向けAI研修・AI導入支援｜SeasideBeer"
  description="松山を拠点に、経営者・管理職向けAI体験、社員研修、業務ごとのAI導入、月次改善を支援します。"
  image="/og.png"
>
  <section class="page-hero corporate-hero">
    <div class="container-wide corporate-head">
      <p class="eyebrow">01 / FOR BUSINESS</p>
      <div class="corporate-title">
        <h1>AIを学ぶ日ではなく、<br /><em>仕事が一つ減る日</em>を。</h1>
        <p>体験、研修、業務設計、制作、改善。知識を渡して終わらず、現場で使える仕組みまで一緒につくります。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="page-hero-actions">
        <a class="button button-primary" href="/contact/">企業向け支援を相談する <span aria-hidden="true">↗</span></a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="service-thesis">
    <div class="container-wide thesis-grid">
      <p class="section-index" data-reveal>THE GAP</p>
      <h2 data-reveal>研修の満足度と、<br />導入の成果は、<br /><em>別のものです。</em></h2>
      <p data-reveal>
        「便利だった」で終われば、翌週には元の仕事へ戻ります。対象業務、入力、確認、共有、改善までを決めて、初めてAIは現場の仕組みになります。
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="offer-section">
    <div class="container-wide">
      <header class="offer-head" data-reveal>
        <p class="section-index">WHAT WE DO</p>
        <h2>必要な地点から、<br />始められます。</h2>
      </header>
      <div class="offer-list">
        <article data-reveal><span>01</span><div><p>EXECUTIVE SESSION</p><h3>経営者・管理職向けAI体験</h3></div><p>自社の業務を題材に、何を任せ、何を人が判断するかを短時間で整理します。</p></article>
        <article data-reveal><span>02</span><div><p>TEAM TRAINING</p><h3>社員向け実践研修</h3></div><p>説明だけで終わらず、参加者が実際の資料や文章をその場で作り、直します。</p></article>
        <article data-reveal><span>03</span><div><p>WORKFLOW BUILD</p><h3>業務ごとのAI導入・制作</h3></div><p>調査、議事録、提案書、広報、Webなど、一つの流れを小さく実装します。</p></article>
        <article data-reveal><span>04</span><div><p>CONTINUOUS IMPROVEMENT</p><h3>月次の改善支援</h3></div><p>使われ方と成果を見直し、手順、テンプレート、確認基準を更新します。</p></article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="method-section">
    <div class="container-wide method-grid">
      <header data-reveal>
        <p class="section-index">DELIVERY SYSTEM</p>
        <h2>現場へ移る、<br /><em>4つの段階。</em></h2>
        <p>大きな構想より、使える一つを先に。成果を確認してから次へ広げます。</p>
      </header>
      <ol class="method-list" data-reveal>
        <li><span>01 / FIND</span><strong>仕事を選ぶ</strong><p>時間、頻度、判断、機密性からAIへ渡す範囲を決める。</p></li>
        <li><span>02 / PROTOTYPE</span><strong>一度、動かす</strong><p>実際の入力と成果物で、小さな試作をつくる。</p></li>
        <li><span>03 / STANDARDIZE</span><strong>手順にする</strong><p>入力例、確認項目、保存先、担当者を明文化する。</p></li>
        <li><span>04 / IMPROVE</span><strong>使って直す</strong><p>時間と品質を確認し、次に減らす仕事を決める。</p></li>
      </ol>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="deliverable-section">
    <div class="container-wide">
      <header data-reveal><p class="section-index">WHAT REMAINS</p><h2>研修後に、<br />残るもの。</h2></header>
      <div class="deliverable-grid" data-reveal>
        <div><span>GUIDE</span><strong>現場向けの手順</strong></div>
        <div><span>TEMPLATE</span><strong>繰り返し使える型</strong></div>
        <div><span>OUTPUT</span><strong>実際の成果物</strong></div>
        <div><span>NEXT</span><strong>次の改善課題</strong></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section-compact">
    <div class="container-wide cta-panel" data-reveal>
      <p class="eyebrow">START WITH ONE WORKFLOW</p>
      <h2>一番時間のかかる仕事を、一つ教えてください。</h2>
      <p>研修が先か、制作が先か、まだ決まっていなくて構いません。対象業務と今の状態から整理します。</p>
      <a class="button button-primary" href="/contact/">相談内容を送る <span aria-hidden="true">↗</span></a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .corporate-hero::before { background: radial-gradient(circle at 34% 34%, var(--tide) 0, var(--blue) 35%, rgba(32,87,245,.03) 70%); }
  .corporate-head { position: relative; z-index: 1; }
  .corporate-title { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.3fr .7fr; gap: 70px; align-items: end; }
  .corporate-title h1 { margin: 0; }
  .corporate-title h1 em { color: var(--tide); font-family: "Noto Serif JP", serif; font-style: normal; font-weight: 500; }
  .corporate-title > p { max-width: 480px; margin: 0 0 12px; color: var(--ink-700); line-height: 2; }
  .service-thesis { padding: clamp(110px,15vw,220px) 0; background: var(--bone); }
  .thesis-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: .28fr 1fr; gap: 30px 80px; }
  .thesis-grid h2 { margin: 0; font-size: clamp(58px,9vw,126px); font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: -.09em; line-height: .98; }
  .thesis-grid h2 em { color: var(--blue); font-family: "Noto Serif JP", serif; font-style: normal; font-weight: 500; }
  .thesis-grid > p:last-child { grid-column: 2; max-width: 660px; margin: 38px 0 0 auto; color: var(--ink-600); line-height: 2; }
  .offer-section { padding: clamp(100px,13vw,180px) 0; }
  .offer-head { display: grid; grid-template-columns: .32fr 1fr; margin-bottom: 72px; }
  .offer-head h2 { margin: 0; font-size: clamp(50px,7vw,98px); font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: -.08em; line-height: 1; }
  .offer-list { border-top: 1px solid var(--line); }
  .offer-list article { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 72px 1fr .8fr; gap: 30px; align-items: center; padding: 34px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); }
  .offer-list article > span,
  .offer-list article div p { color: var(--blue); font-size: 8px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: .14em; }
  .offer-list article div p { margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .offer-list h3 { margin: 0; font-size: clamp(22px,2.5vw,34px); font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: -.04em; }
  .offer-list article > p { margin: 0; color: var(--ink-600); font-size: 13px; }
  .method-section { padding: clamp(100px,13vw,180px) 0; color: white; background: var(--ink); }
  .method-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: .75fr 1.25fr; gap: clamp(60px,10vw,150px); }
  .method-grid header .section-index { color: var(--tide); }
  .method-grid header h2 { margin: 0; font-size: clamp(50px,7vw,96px); font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: -.08em; line-height: 1; }
  .method-grid header h2 em { color: var(--tide); font-family: "Noto Serif JP", serif; font-style: normal; }
  .method-grid header > p:last-child { margin: 34px 0 0; color: rgba(255,255,255,.48); }
  .method-list { margin: 0; padding: 0; border-top: 1px solid var(--line-invert); list-style: none; }
  .method-list li { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 120px 1fr; gap: 8px 24px; padding: 26px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line-invert); }
  .method-list span { color: var(--tide); font-size: 8px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: .14em; }
  .method-list strong { font-size: 20px; font-weight: 600; }
  .method-list p { grid-column: 2; margin: 0; color: rgba(255,255,255,.48); font-size: 12px; }
  .deliverable-section { padding: clamp(100px,13vw,180px) 0; background: var(--blue); color: white; }
  .deliverable-section header { display: flex; align-items: flex-end; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 70px; }
  .deliverable-section .section-index { color: var(--tide); }
  .deliverable-section h2 { margin: 0; font-size: clamp(54px,8vw,110px); font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: -.085em; line-height: 1; }
  .deliverable-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4,1fr); border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.28); border-left: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.28); }
  .deliverable-grid div { min-height: 250px; padding: 24px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.28); border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.28); }
  .deliverable-grid span { color: var(--tide); font-size: 8px; letter-spacing: .16em; }
  .deliverable-grid strong { display: block; margin-top: 120px; font-size: 18px; }
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .corporate-title,
    .method-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .corporate-title { gap: 34px; }
    .thesis-grid,
    .offer-head { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 28px; }
    .thesis-grid > p:last-child { grid-column: 1; }
    .deliverable-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2,1fr); }
  }
  @media (max-width: 680px) {
    .offer-list article { grid-template-columns: 40px 1fr; gap: 18px; }
    .offer-list article > p { grid-column: 2; }
    .method-list li { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .method-list p { grid-column: 1; }
    .deliverable-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .deliverable-grid div { min-height: 180px; }
    .deliverable-grid strong { margin-top: 74px; }
  }
</style>
